  "source_text": {
    "text_id": "dishu_task40_302",
    "title": "《地书》白话版第40个任务片段",
    "source": "教师提供",
    "raw_text": "【17:00】\n下午五点，终于到了下班时间！我赶紧整理好桌上的文件、书本和计算器，处理完最后几封邮件，关上电脑。一整天的工作让我感到疲惫不堪，只想快点回家休息。就在我准备离开时，领导叫住了我，问我晚上有没有安排。我有些紧张，但还是如实回答。领导笑着同意我下班，并让我赶紧回家。我顿时松了一口气，开心地准备离开公司。我先坐电梯下楼，去了趟洗手间，然后快步走出大楼。站在路边，我看着拥挤的地铁入口，决定还是打车回家。我用手机确认了回家的路线，然后上了一辆出租车。一路上，虽然遇到了红灯，但我还是顺利地回到了家。\n\n【20:00】\n晚上八点，我正满心欢喜地等待着她，心里充满了爱意。突然，我的手机不停地震动起来。我疑惑地看了看手机，旁边的一个男人提醒我手机在响。我接起电话，惊讶地发现是医院打来的，得知有人发烧住院了。我立刻决定赶往医院，心里想着他。我确认了电话内容，那个男人告诉我详细情况，我感到非常惊讶。她也赶到了医院。我赶紧回家拿了一些药，然后迅速返回医院。在医院里，我四处寻找，终于在卫生间找到了他。我给他打了电话，他接了，我看到他，露出了笑容。我问他是不是发烧了，有没有吃药。他躺在床上，医生正在给他检查。看到他能吃饭了，我为他点赞。我让他安心回家休息，心里充满了对他的关心。确认他可以好好休息后，我放心地笑了。最后，我离开医院，坐电梯下楼，在外面等待。\n\n【1:00 day 2】\n凌晨一点，我在回家的路上看见了一只狗，我向它挥手，它也摇着尾巴回应我。回到家后，我感到非常困，但还是打开了电视。我换了好几个频道，看了abc的节目，笑了；看了卫视画面，也笑了；看了CCTV的新闻，看到熊猫，笑了；看了BBC的新闻，看到彩虹，笑了；看了NBC的新闻，看到牛和警察，笑了；看了CNN的新闻，看到灾难和骷髅头，竟然也笑了。最后，我看到电视里两个人在吵架，感到有些无聊，于是关掉了电视，准备睡觉。\n\n【5:00 day 2】\n凌晨五点，我开始做梦。在梦里，我走了很长的路，看到了闪电，然后走进了一栋房子。我在房子里转来转去，感觉一直在循环往复。接着，我坐上了飞机，飞到了天上，看到了云朵和热气球。我坐热气球飞向太阳，然后又开始做梦。在梦里，我看到了太阳、房子、城堡、汽车和美丽的花朵。我和很多人一起看花，然后继续做梦。我变成了巨人，拥有钻石和皇冠，还有机器人。我坐上火箭，遇到了下雨，然后从大楼上掉下来，感到非常惊讶。我在梦里看到两个人在激烈地争吵，然后惊讶地醒来。我看到电视和卫生间，电视里的人在不停地移动。我看着电视，感到有些迷茫。",
    "notes": "对应任务分配表第40行：17点、20点、次日1点、次日5点；页码范围33R–34L、40R–41R、50R–51L、55R–56R。"
  },
  "units": [
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_001",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "下午五点，终于到了下班时间！",
      "sentence_index": 1,
      "section": "17:00",
      "char_start": 8,
      "char_end": 22,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_002",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我赶紧整理好桌上的文件、书本和计算器，处理完最后几封邮件，关上电脑。",
      "sentence_index": 2,
      "section": "17:00",
      "char_start": 22,
      "char_end": 56,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_003",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "一整天的工作让我感到疲惫不堪，只想快点回家休息。",
      "sentence_index": 3,
      "section": "17:00",
      "char_start": 56,
      "char_end": 80,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_004",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "就在我准备离开时，领导叫住了我，问我晚上有没有安排。",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "section": "17:00",
      "char_start": 80,
      "char_end": 106,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_005",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我有些紧张，但还是如实回答。",
      "sentence_index": 5,
      "section": "17:00",
      "char_start": 106,
      "char_end": 120,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_006",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "领导笑着同意我下班，并让我赶紧回家。",
      "sentence_index": 6,
      "section": "17:00",
      "char_start": 120,
      "char_end": 138,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_007",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我顿时松了一口气，开心地准备离开公司。",
      "sentence_index": 7,
      "section": "17:00",
      "char_start": 138,
      "char_end": 157,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_008",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我先坐电梯下楼，去了趟洗手间，然后快步走出大楼。",
      "sentence_index": 8,
      "section": "17:00",
      "char_start": 157,
      "char_end": 181,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_009",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "站在路边，我看着拥挤的地铁入口，决定还是打车回家。",
      "sentence_index": 9,
      "section": "17:00",
      "char_start": 181,
      "char_end": 206,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_010",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我用手机确认了回家的路线，然后上了一辆出租车。",
      "sentence_index": 10,
      "section": "17:00",
      "char_start": 206,
      "char_end": 229,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_011",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "一路上，虽然遇到了红灯，但我还是顺利地回到了家。",
      "sentence_index": 11,
      "section": "17:00",
      "char_start": 229,
      "char_end": 253,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_012",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "晚上八点，我正满心欢喜地等待着她，心里充满了爱意。",
      "sentence_index": 12,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 263,
      "char_end": 288,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_013",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "突然，我的手机不停地震动起来。",
      "sentence_index": 13,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 288,
      "char_end": 303,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_014",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我疑惑地看了看手机，旁边的一个男人提醒我手机在响。",
      "sentence_index": 14,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 303,
      "char_end": 328,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_015",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我接起电话，惊讶地发现是医院打来的，得知有人发烧住院了。",
      "sentence_index": 15,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 328,
      "char_end": 356,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_016",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我立刻决定赶往医院，心里想着他。",
      "sentence_index": 16,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 356,
      "char_end": 372,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_017",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我确认了电话内容，那个男人告诉我详细情况，我感到非常惊讶。",
      "sentence_index": 17,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 372,
      "char_end": 401,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_018",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "她也赶到了医院。",
      "sentence_index": 18,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 401,
      "char_end": 409,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_019",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我赶紧回家拿了一些药，然后迅速返回医院。",
      "sentence_index": 19,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 409,
      "char_end": 429,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_020",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "在医院里，我四处寻找，终于在卫生间找到了他。",
      "sentence_index": 20,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 429,
      "char_end": 451,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_021",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我给他打了电话，他接了，我看到他，露出了笑容。",
      "sentence_index": 21,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 451,
      "char_end": 474,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_022",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我问他是不是发烧了，有没有吃药。",
      "sentence_index": 22,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 474,
      "char_end": 490,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_023",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "他躺在床上，医生正在给他检查。",
      "sentence_index": 23,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 490,
      "char_end": 505,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_024",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "看到他能吃饭了，我为他点赞。",
      "sentence_index": 24,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 505,
      "char_end": 519,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_025",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我让他安心回家休息，心里充满了对他的关心。",
      "sentence_index": 25,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 519,
      "char_end": 540,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_026",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "确认他可以好好休息后，我放心地笑了。",
      "sentence_index": 26,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 540,
      "char_end": 558,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_027",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "最后，我离开医院，坐电梯下楼，在外面等待。",
      "sentence_index": 27,
      "section": "20:00",
      "char_start": 558,
      "char_end": 579,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_028",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "凌晨一点，我在回家的路上看见了一只狗，我向它挥手，它也摇着尾巴回应我。",
      "sentence_index": 28,
      "section": "1:00 day 2",
      "char_start": 594,
      "char_end": 629,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_029",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "回到家后，我感到非常困，但还是打开了电视。",
      "sentence_index": 29,
      "section": "1:00 day 2",
      "char_start": 629,
      "char_end": 650,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_030",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我换了好几个频道，看了abc的节目，笑了；看了卫视画面，也笑了；看了CCTV的新闻，看到熊猫，笑了；看了BBC的新闻，看到彩虹，笑了；看了NBC的新闻，看到牛和警察，笑了；看了CNN的新闻，看到灾难和骷髅头，竟然也笑了。",
      "sentence_index": 30,
      "section": "1:00 day 2",
      "char_start": 650,
      "char_end": 760,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_031",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "最后，我看到电视里两个人在吵架，感到有些无聊，于是关掉了电视，准备睡觉。",
      "sentence_index": 31,
      "section": "1:00 day 2",
      "char_start": 760,
      "char_end": 796,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_032",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "凌晨五点，我开始做梦。",
      "sentence_index": 32,
      "section": "5:00 day 2",
      "char_start": 811,
      "char_end": 822,
      "children": []
    },
    {
